						 <p>It’s great to finally be able to relax and know that those spooky aliens are just trying to promote forklift safety after all. Mulder would have such blue balls.</p> <p>As an inconsequential aside, and this may be an instance of that chromatic adaptation phenomenon that sparked the “#thedress” meme, but the ship in the pictograms looks markedly brown/rust color to me, not gray.</p> 
