					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7064870#post-3921886</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-7064870/scp-4048#post-3921886</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 22 Aug 2018 16:04:13 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>PRodgerMMath</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4490533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This sentence from the containment procedures:</p> <blockquote> <p>Civilians entering these programs are to have their backgrounds checked for previous forklift certification that was previously revoked.</p> </blockquote> <p>Seems to be in conflict with this one from the description:</p> <blockquote> <p>In addition, all evidence that the target was ever forklift certified will be voided in some way during this event.</p> </blockquote> <p>Surely the background check won't find anything if all the evidence is gone? Unless I'm misunderstanding what's meant by &quot;voided&quot; here.</p> <p>Also, I don't get the flawed teaching. If people fail their test then their certification is revoked, they have good reason to believe it actually happened, and soon enough you've got headlines like &quot;Aliens Revoked My Forklift Certification!!&quot;. If people pass then they can easily shrug the whole thing off as a dream.</p> <p>That stuff aside, I really love the concept of the Health and Safety Aliens taking over through Improved Forklift Operation.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
