						 <p>A goofy idea I came up with a while back, after I saw a meme that said something along the lines of &quot;if we found aliens, what would we do? Leave them alone, help them prosper, nuke them, or make sure their forklift operators are following OSHA regulations?&quot;</p> <p>Thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414239&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542082658" alt="Gabriel Jade" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414239)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/gabriel-jade" >Gabriel Jade</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sir-baubius" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2200357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542082658" alt="Sir Baubius" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2200357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sir-baubius" >Sir Baubius</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/prototype-toaster" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3512728&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542082658" alt="Prototype_Toaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3512728)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/prototype-toaster" >Prototype_Toaster</a></span> for critique. Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2303803&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542082658" alt="Cyantreuse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2303803)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cyantreuse" >Cyantreuse</a></span> for image help, and CuteGirl's dad (in chat) for forklift help.</p> <p>Edit: for the record, both images are by me</p> <p>Edit: I'd like to bring attention to a <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-4048">Chinese translation</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ashausesall" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1546989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542082658" alt="ashausesall" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1546989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ashausesall" >ashausesall</a></span></p> <p>Edit: I'd also like to bring attention to a <a href="http://ja.scp-wiki.net/scp-4048">Japanese translation</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2767088&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1542082658" alt="Hasuma_S" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2767088)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/hasuma-s" >Hasuma_S</a></span></p> 
